Define all the Parameters

#define states
E <- 759000
V <- 83300
A <- 7400
B <- 1750
C <- 0
D <- 0
Ex <- 63000

states = c(E = E, V = V, A = A, B = B, C = C, D = D, Ex = Ex)

#define parameters

## Death Flows
muBaseline <- 1/69 #1 over life expectancy (79) starting at age 10 
muInjection <- .0062
mu_E <- muBaseline
mu_V <- muBaseline
mu_A <- muBaseline + muInjection
mu_B <- muBaseline + muInjection
mu_C <- muBaseline + muInjection
mu_D <- muBaseline + muInjection
mu_Ex <- muBaseline

## Initiation Function Parameters
beta <- .625
RR_Init <- 6.865
RR_MAT <- .591

average_assisted <- 2
m <- 1/average_assisted

## other flows
injection_cessation <- .1

e_v <- 0.025
v_e <- 0.2
a_c <- 0
c_a <- 266/365
b_d <- 0
d_b <- 266/365
a_ex <- injection_cessation
b_ex <- injection_cessation
c_ex <- injection_cessation
d_ex <- injection_cessation

parameters = c(mu_E = mu_E, mu_V = mu_V, mu_A = mu_A, mu_B = mu_B, mu_C = mu_C, mu_D = mu_D, mu_Ex = mu_Ex, beta = beta, RR_Init = RR_Init, RR_MAT = RR_MAT, e_v = e_v, v_e = v_e, a_c = a_c, c_a = c_a, b_d = b_d, d_b = d_b)

#define time
t = seq(0,1000, by = 1)

result <- ode(y = states, times = t, func = de_fun, parms = parameters)
result_df <- data.frame(result)

Fitting Free Variables

Okee, so we have variables we need to figure out. These plots can be used to match up to values in the parameters table.

OAT thresholds

The OAT enroll values represent the A -> C and B -> D transition rates for achieving that OAT coverage

OAT_enroll <- 0.095

parameters_ten <- c(mu_E = mu_E, mu_V = mu_V, mu_A = mu_A, mu_B = mu_B, mu_C = mu_C, mu_D = mu_D, mu_Ex = mu_Ex, beta = beta, RR_Init = RR_Init, RR_MAT = RR_MAT, e_v = e_v, v_e = v_e, a_c = OAT_enroll, c_a = c_a, b_d = OAT_enroll, d_b = d_b)

result <- ode(y = states, times = t, func = de_fun, parms = parameters_ten)
result_df <- data.frame(result)

OAT_enroll <- 0.21

parameters_twenty <- c(mu_E = mu_E, mu_V = mu_V, mu_A = mu_A, mu_B = mu_B, mu_C = mu_C, mu_D = mu_D, mu_Ex = mu_Ex, beta = beta, RR_Init = RR_Init, RR_MAT = RR_MAT, e_v = e_v, v_e = v_e, a_c = OAT_enroll, c_a = c_a, b_d = OAT_enroll, d_b = d_b)

result <- ode(y = states, times = t, func = de_fun, parms = parameters_twenty)
result_df <- data.frame(result)
